# Cursor MCP Configuration for Discovery Agent

This project includes an MCP server that Cursor can use.

## To Enable in Cursor:

Add this to your Cursor MCP settings (Cursor Settings → Features → MCP):

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "discovery-agent": {
      "command": "python3",
      "args": [
        "/Users/codymenefee/Documents/Projects/offBench/mcp-servers/clients/shopify/offbench-shopify/mcp/src/main.py",
        "--stdio"
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

## Available Tools:

- find_project_folders() - List available test scenarios
- ingest_documents(project_id) - Load discovery docs
- analyze_discovery(project_id) - Analyze and score confidence
- get_template(type) - Load templates
- fill_template(project_id, type) - Generate deliverables
- extract_open_questions(project_id) - Get clarifying questions
- update_project_context(project_id, info) - Add context
- recalculate_confidence(project_id) - Re-analyze

